 Release Info:
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 The pack will include TOMB RAIDER Legend and TOMB RAIDER Anniversary,
 both newly remastered in HD quality, as well as TOMB RAIDER Underworld,
 previously released on PlayStation 3. A number of items were also created
 exclusively for this pack, including a THE TOMB RAIDER TRILOGY
 PlayStation 3 theme pack, the official Lara Croft female Home avatar
 outfit, the Viking Thrall male Home avatar outfit and a collection of
 "making of" trailers in HD for the entire series, a must for any
 TOMB RAIDER fan.


 Notes:
 ~~~~~~

 First working english release wins .. there is no need to dupe every
 release with one from a different region. There are no region locks.
 And yes, also games bought in the USA can be multi and played on Euro
 consoles (and vice versa!).
 Therefore we don't tag our releases with a source region, and we encourage
 other groups to do the same and siteops to deny such useless dupes and
 adjust rules.
